1. *Majmun* je penjao po drvetu. (The *monkey* was climbing the tree.)
2. Videla sam velikog *majmuna* u zoo vrtu. (I saw a big *monkey* in the zoo.)
3. Ne znam da li bih se smejao kao *majmun* ili plakao. (I don't know whether to laugh like a *monkey* or cry.)
4. *Majmunica* je bila jako ljupka. (The *female monkey* was very cute.)
5. Moj sin obožava da gleda crtać o *majmunima*. (My son loves watching cartoons about *monkeys*.)
6. On je bio vest u penjanju kao pravi *majmun*. (He was skilled in climbing like a real *monkey*.)
7. Njih dvoje su se ponašali kao *majmuni* u cirkusu. (The two of them were acting like *monkeys* in the circus.)
8. Moraš da budeš oprezan kada hodaš po šumi jer ima mnogo divljih *majmuna*. (You have to be careful when walking in the forest because there are many wild *monkeys*.)
9. Ona je bila toliko besna da je vikala kao *majmun*. (She was so angry that she was screaming like a *monkey*.)
10. *Majmunski* hleb je bio omiljeni obrok ovih životinja. (*Monkey* bread was the favorite meal of these animals.)